data.description: Welcome to this Nicely Manicured Corner Lot, landscaped curb appeal Cozy 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in Rosamond, a Must See! It is a Great Single Story Starter Home for First-Time Buyers or Investors. Features carpeting and tile flooring, Window covered Blinds throughout the home, Solar Panels installed by Sunrun Solar company with a low monthly rate of $117.89, Vivint Security System and Doorbell Camera, gas fireplace in living room, formal dining area, with sliding door that leads to a covered patio offering privacy for entertaining, with a nice size Storage Shed in spacious rear yard.  Stainless steel kitchen appliances included in sale, stove, mounted microwave and dishwasher complimented by upgrades as follows; Stainless Steel double sink, granite counter tops, recessed lighting and cabinets. Breakfast bar opens up to an additional living area with a second slider door exiting to the side yard, the interior two car garage door is also off of this space and Front Entry. The master bedroom has a third sliding door for access to the back yard. Nearby shopping, banking, schools, and parks. Home is being Sold As Is.
